18#include "PDFModulusGF.h"
19#include <stdexcept>
20
21namespace ZXing {
22namespace Pdf417 {
23
24ModulusGF::ModulusGF(int modulus, int generator) :
25 _modulus(modulus),
26 _zero(*this, { 0 }),
27 _one(*this, { 1 })
28{
29 _expTable.resize(modulus, 0);
30 _logTable.resize(modulus, 0);
31 int x = 1;
32 for (int i = 0; i < modulus; i++) {
33 _expTable[i] = x;
34 x = (x * generator) % modulus;
35 }
36 for (int i = 0; i < modulus - 1; i++) {
37 _logTable[_expTable[i]] = i;
38 }
39 // logTable[0] == 0 but this should never be used
40}
41
42ModulusPoly
43ModulusGF::buildMonomial(int degree, int coefficient) const
44{
45 if (degree < 0) {
46 throw std::invalid_argument("degree < 0");
47 }
48 if (coefficient == 0) {
49 return _zero;
50 }
51 std::vector<int> coefficients(degree + 1, 0);
52 coefficients[0] = coefficient;
53 return ModulusPoly(*this, coefficients);
54}
